Enum CardReaderManager.ChipAndPinSoftwareUpdateStatus

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<CardReaderManager.ChipAndPinSoftwareUpdateStatus>
      • com.paypal.merchant.sdk.CardReaderManager.ChipAndPinSoftwareUpdateStatus
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<CardReaderManager.ChipAndPinSoftwareUpdateStatus>
    Enclosing interface:
    CardReaderManager

    public static enum CardReaderManager.ChipAndPinSoftwareUpdateStatus
extends Enum<CardReaderManager.ChipAndPinSoftwareUpdateStatus>
    The list of possible status messages when initiating an update of the PayPal integrated Chip & Pin card reader.
